Blake Lively=E2=80=99s legal complaint against co-star
Justin Baldoni and his team of operators exposes the sinister subset of the=
 crisis communications industry that seeks to attack and misinform, even as=
 Lively=E2=80=99s own tactics, and the role of notorious publicist Stephani=
e Jones, come further into focus.

Matthew Belloni ( https://puck.news/author/matthew-belloni/?utm_campaign=3D=
What+I%27m+Hearing+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F23%2F24%29&utm_content=3DWhat+I%27=
m+Hearing+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F24%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_so=
