line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><em>A little hodgepodge of responses, from Disn=
ey=E2=80=99s Trump
settlement to Amazon=E2=80=99s short theatrical window for =E2=80=98Red One=
,=E2=80=99 to agent Doug Johnson=E2=80=99s defection from CAA to WME=E2=80=
=A6</em></p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><em>=C2=A0</em></p><p =
style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=E2=80=9CInteresting that you refer t=
o the <strong>Stephanopoulos</strong> mistake as a =E2=80=98fleeting error=
=E2=80=99 when he repeated it 10 times during the interview with <strong>Na=
ncy Mace </strong>and doubled down on it in subsequent interviews with othe=
r news organizations. Note the timing of the
settlement, shortly after George was ordered to sit for a deposition. My gu=
ess is the ABC lawyers saw the handwriting on the wall.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94<=
em>An executive</em></p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p>=
<p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=E2=80=9CThe other thing that Amaz=
on neglects to mention is that [<em>Red One</em>] auto-played after the <em=
>TNF</em> game. I know that can=E2=80=99t account for all the views, but it=
 certainly helps.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94<em>Another executive</em></p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:
0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=
=99s not news that tech companies are raping and pillaging Hollywood. The o=
nly surprising fact continues to be how we are all willingly letting them d=
o it.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94<em>An actor/filmmaker</em>=C2=A0=C2=A0</p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">=E2=80=9C=
You didn=E2=80=99t mention the biggest reason CAA agents are stuck there: e=
quity. It=E2=80=99s easy for Doug to leave for [a rival like] WME when you =
don=E2=80=99t have any big equity stake you
are giving up. But if you become a manager [and don=E2=80=99t =E2=80=98comp=
ete=E2=80=99 with CAA] you can keep that equity.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94<em>A ma=
nager</em></p></div>
