tions for L.A. dining over the break=E2=80=A6</em></p><p style=3D"margin:0;=
margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">I st=
ay in L.A. over the holidays for many reasons: no travel stress, great weat=
her, and empty freeways. But my No. 1 motivation? The chance to eat at some=
 of the city=E2=80=99s best restaurants. My current picks:</p><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:
0px;"><strong>The Benjamin</strong>: It=E2=80=99s the holidays, so L.A.=E2=
=80=99s current culinary hotspot won=E2=80=99t be packed with all the Holly=
wood people you don=E2=80=99t want to see. Show up early to grab a coveted =
seat at the bar, which is held for walk-ins. And order the burger and the d=
eviled eggs.=C2=A0=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0=
</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><strong>Moo=E2=80=99s Craft Ba=
rbecue</strong>: You don=E2=80=99t have to go to Texas, Kansas City, or Nor=
th Carolina for some of the
best BBQ in America. No reservations at this Eastside spot, so a holiday tr=
ip is perfect. Get the burger along with classics like brisket, sausages, a=
nd ribs.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p sty=
le=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><strong>Holbox</strong>: This counter-se=
rvice Mexican seafood spot downtown serves some of the best mariscos in the=
 city. Perfect for before or after catching <strong>Sutton Foster</strong> =
in <em>Once Upon a Mattress</em> at The
Ahmanson.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p st=
yle=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><strong>Dunsmoor</strong>: Yes, this is=
 in Glassell Park. Yes, Glassell Park is in L.A. Picture driving to Dodger =
Stadium and forgetting to get off the freeway for a few exits. The order is=
 simple: baby albacore, Edna=E2=80=99s sour milk cornbread, Aunt Emmy=E2=80=
=99s pork and green chili stew, Carolina gold rice, mushroom-crusted pork c=
hop, rib eye.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p styl=
e=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;"><strong>Quarter Sheets</strong>: Echo Par=
k=E2=80=99s sensation is redefining a dream combo of pizza <em>and</em> des=
serts in L.A. The menu is ever-changing, so just get whatever <strong>Aaron=
</strong> and <strong>Hannah</strong> are serving and thank me later.</p><p=
 style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;"><em=
